>How has this lesson changed your view of temperance? </div><div class="t m400 x8c h1a y511 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m3d3 xe h1a y64a ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">After studying this week&apos;s lesson, how would you explain </div><div class="t m8a xe h1a y64b ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the Christian concept of self-control to a curious neighbor? </div><div class="t m3f7 x4c h1a y64c ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: True temperance is refusing to use or do any-</div><div class="t m568 x4c h1a y513 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thing harmful and using or doing in moderation those things </div><div class="t m35f x4c h1a y4a5 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which are good. It is motivated by our love for God and fellow </div><div class="t m5fe x4c h1a y3e0 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">human beings. And we receive the strength for it from our </div><div class="t m32e x4c h1a y4a6 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heavenly Father. </div><div class="t m1ea x2a h1a y64d ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Did you give a Thirteenth Sabbath Offering second </div><div class="t m27a x30 h1a yf7 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">quarter of 1987? </div><div class="t m431 x2a h1a y64e ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">If so, you helped to build this girls&apos; dormitory at Nile </div><div class="t m185 x30 h1a yf9 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Union Academy in Egypt. </div><div class="t m5ff x2a h1a yfa ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The attached fields, not part of an organized divi-</div><div class="t m566 x30 h1a y64f ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sion, are union territories directed from the General </div><div class="t m443 x30 h1a y650 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Conference headquarters. </div><div class="t m600 x2a h1a y651 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Help them again this Thirteenth Sabbath. </div><div class="t m601 x70 h1a y651 ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">See back </div><div class="t m4f7 x30 h1a y652 ff5 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cover </div><div class="t m54b x58 h1a y366 ff1 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">61 </div></div><div